thread.title: Lynx capture 3rd title in 5 years with 69-52 win in Game 5

title: Lynx capture 3rd title in 5 years with 69-52 win in Game 5
text:
> Indiana Lynx capture 3rd title in 5 years with 69-52 win in Game 5 Minnesota Lynx players celebrate a play against the Indiana Fever in the first half of Game 5 of the WNBA basketball finals, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015, in Minneapolis.
